FUPFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if APERIOD=1 and (AENDT > TR01EDT + 27 days or AENDT is missing); or if APERIOD=2 and (AENDT > TR02EDT + 27 days or AENDT is missing); missing otherwise
MDOSREF Computation
Set to 'Vaccination 1' if 1. missing < ADSL.TR01SDT <= ASTDT < ADSL.DOSE2DT or 2. missing < ADSL.TR01SDT <= ASTDT and ADSL.DOS2DT is missing and (ADSL.TR02SDT is missing or missing < ASTDT < ADSL.TR02SDT), Set to 'Vaccination 2' if 1. missing < ADSL.DOS2DT <= ASTDT < ADSL.TR02SDT or 2. missing < ADSL.DOS2DT <= ASTDT and ADSL.TR02SDT is missing, Set to 'OL Vaccination 1' if 1. missing < ADSL.TR02SDT <= ASTDT<ADSL.OLDOS2DT or 2. missing < ADSL.TR02SDT <= ASTDT and ADSL.OLDOS2DT is missing, Set to 'OL Vaccination 2' if missing < ADSL.OLDOS2DT <= ASTDT
MRDSTDY Computation
Set to ASTDT – TR01SDT + 1 if MDOSREF='Vaccination 1', Set to ASTDT – DOS2DT + 1 if MDOSREF='Vaccination 2', Set to ASTDT – TR02SDT + 1 if MDOSREF='OL Vaccination 1', Set to ASTDT – OLDOS2DT + 1 if MDOSREF='OL Vaccination 2'
ONTRTFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if APERIOD=1 and (ASTDT <= TR01EDT + 27 days) and (AENDT >= TR01SDT or AENDT is missing); or if ASTDT is missing and (AENDT >= TR01SDT or AENDT is missing); or if APERIOD=2 and (ASTDT <= TR02EDT + 27 days) and (AENDT >= TR02SDT or AENDT is missing); or if ASTDT is missing and (AENDT >= TR02SDT or AENDT is missing); or missing otherwise
PREFL Computation
"Y" if ASTDT < TR01SDT or ASTDT is missing; missing otherwise
APERIOD Computation
Set to 2 if non-missing AP02SSDT<=DVSTDTC, Otherwise, Set to 1
DVSIG Computation
Set to SUPPDV.QVAL where SUPPDV.QNAM='DVSIG'
DVTERM1 Computation
Set to SUPPDV.QVAL where SUPPDV.QNAM='DVTERM1'
BOD Computation
Set to the first ADEFF.ADT where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and APERIOD = 1 and . < ADT <= EFFCODT per USUBJID, Set to missing, otherwise
BOI Computation
Set to the first ADEFF.ADT where PARAMCD='COVIDA' and APERIOD = 1 and . < ADT <= EFFCODT, Set to ADEFF.ADT where PARAMCD = 'ASYMPINF' and APERIOD = 1 and . < ADT <= EFFCODT if ADEFF.ADT where PARAMCD='COVIDA' per USUBJID is missing, Set to missing, otherwise
ANL01FL Computation
Set to 'Y' to the record with maximum of AVAL where paramcd = BOD28D per USUBJID
ANL01FL Computation
Set to 'Y' to the record with maximum of AVAL where paramcd = BOI28D per USUBJID
BOD Computation
For PARAMCD = “BOD7D”: Set to 0 if EVENTMO > AWRANGEN or ADT=missing Set to 3 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and not missing (ADSL.DTHDT) and (DTHDT - ADT + 1) <= 7. Set to 2 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and USUBJID is in HO and 1 <= (any non-missing numeric HO.HOSTDTC – ADT + 1) <= 7 Set to 1 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' For PARAMCD = “BOD28D”: Set to 0 if EVENTMO > AWRANGEN or ADT=missing Set to 3 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and not missing (ADSL.DTHDT) and (DTHDT - ADT + 1) <= 28. Set to 2 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and USUBJID is in HO and 1 <= (any non-missing numeric HO.HOSTDTC – ADT + 1) <= 28 Set to 1 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA'
BOI Computation
For PARAMCD = “BOI7D”: Set to 0 if EVENTMO > AWRANGEN or ADT=missing Set to 3 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and not missing (ADSL.DTHDT) and (DTHDT-ADT+1) <= 7. Set to 2 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD='COVIDA' and USUBJID is in HO and 1<=(any non-missing numeric HO.HOSTDTC - ADT + 1) <= 7 Set to 1 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' Set to 0.5 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'ASYMPINF' For PARAMCD = “BOI28D”: Set to 0 if EVENTMO > AWRANGEN or ADT=missing Set to 3 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' and not missing (ADSL.DTHDT) and (DTHDT-ADT+1) <= 28 Set to 2 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD='COVIDA' and USUBJID is in HO and 1<=(any non-missing numeric HO.HOSTDTC - ADT + 1) <= 28 Set to 1 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'COVIDA' Set to 0.5 if ADEFF.AVALC = 'Y' where PARAMCD = 'ASYMPINF'
BOD Computation
Set EVENTMO = ADT - RANDDT+1)/30.4375 and create # of records per USUBJID per PARAMCD based on EVENTMO: Create 4 records if EVENTMO >= 18: AWRANGE = 'Randomization through 6 Months', ' After 6 Months through 12 Months', ' After 12 Months through 18 Months', ' After 18 Months through Completion' Create 3 records if EVENTMO >= 12: AWRANGE = 'Randomization through 6 Months', ' After 6 Months through 12 Months', ' After 12 Months through 18 Months' Create 2 records if EVENTMO >= 6: AWRANGE = 'Randomization through 6 Months', ' After 6 Months through 12 Months' Create 1 records, otherwise: AWRANGE = 'Randomization through 6 Months'
BOI Computation
Set EVENTMO = ADT - RANDDT+1)/30.4375 and create # of records per USUBJID per PARAMCD based on EVENTMO: Create 5 records If EVENTMO >=13 or ADT is missing: AWRANGE= 'Baseline through Month 1', 'After Month 1 through Month 2', 'After Month 2 through Month 7', 'After Month 7 through Month 13', and 'After Month 13 through Month 25' Create 4 records if EVENTMO >=7: AWRANGE= 'Baseline through Month 1', 'After Month 1 through Month 2', 'After Month 2 through Month 7', and 'After Month 7 through Month 13' Create 3 records if EVENTMO >=2: AWRANGE='Baseline through Month 1', 'After Month 1 through Month 2', and 'After Month 2 through Month 7' Create 2 records if EVENTMO >=1: AWRANGE = 'Baseline through Month 1' and 'After Month 1 through Month 2'. Create 1 record, otherwise: AWRANGE = 'Baseline through Month 1'
BOD Computation
Set to 1 if AWRANGE='Randomization through 6 Months'; Set to 2 if AWRANGE='After 6 Months through 12 Months'; Set to 3 if AWRANGE='After 12 Months through 18 Months'; Set to 4 if AWRANGE='After 18 Months through Completion';
BOI Computation
Set to 1 if AWRANGE='Baseline through Month 1'; Set to 2 if AWRANGE='After Month 1 through Month 2'; Set to 3 if AWRANGE='After Month 2 through Month 7'; Set to 4 if AWRANGE='After Month 7 through Month 13'; Set to 5 if AWRANGE='After Month 13 through Month 25';
ADT Computation
Step 1: Convert date part of FADTC to numeric if source data are from FAEF Convert date part of VSDTC to numeric if source data are from VS Step 2: Keep all records that occurred on or after COVID-19 (ADT from step 1 >= COVIDADT)
AGAPFL Computation
1) Sort the data by subject (SUBJID) and ADT 2) Set to 'Y' if ADT - last ADT > 28 and set 'Y' to all records on or after the ADT per subject
ANL01FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if HOSPFL ne 'Y' and ARELTG2N = 1 and AGAPFL ne 'Y'
ARELTPG1 Computation
Set to '<= 14 Days after COVID-19 Onset Date' if 1 <= ARELTPTN <= 15 Set to '> 14 Days after COVID-19 Onset Date' if ARELTPTN > 15
ARELTPG2 Computation
Set to '<= 28 Days after COVID-19 Onset Date' if 1 <= ARELTPTN <= 29 Set to '> 28 Days after COVID-19 Onset Date' if ARELTPTN > 29
ARELTPT Computation
Set to 'Day ' || ARELTPTN
ARELTPTN Computation
Set to ADT - COVIDADT + 1
AVAL.VS Computation
Set to VS.VSSTRESN
AVAL.FA Computation
Set to 0 if AVALC = 'NONE' 1 if AVALC = 'MILD' 2 if AVALC = 'MODERATE' 3 if AVALC = 'SEVERE'
AVALC.VS Computation
Set to Null
AVALC.FA Computation
Set to FAEF.FASTRESC
COVIDADT Computation
Set to first ADEFF.ADT where PARAMCD='COVIDA' and APERIOD = 1 and . < ADT <= EFFCODT per subject
FASYMPFL Computation
Set to 'Y' to the first ADT where PARAMCD ne (TEMP or OXYSAT) and AVAL > 0
HOSPFL Computation
Set to 'Y' per subject (USUBJID) if HO.HOOCCUR = 'Y' and .z < COVIDADT <= HOSTDTC where HOTERM = 'HOSPITAL' or 'ADMITTED TO ICU'
PARAM Computation
Set to VS.VSTEST || ' ( ||VSSTRESU|| ')' if source data from VS. Please add space between VSTEST and VSSTRESU Set to FAEF.FAOBJ if source data from FAEF. If FAOBJ='Myalgia', re-code it as 'Muscle Aches (Myalgia)' and if FAOBJ='Rhinorrhea', re-code it as 'Runny Nose (Rhinorrhea)'
PARCAT1 Computation
Set to 'Oxygen Saturation or Temperature' if PARAMCD = 'TEMP' or 'OXYSAT' Set to 'Non Oxygen Saturation and Temperature'
SRCDOM Computation
Set to 'FAEF' if source data are from FAEF Set to 'VS' if source data are from VS
SRCSEQ Computation
FAEF.FASEQ if source data are from FAEF VS.VSSEQ if source data are from VS
SRCVAR Computation
Set to 'FASTRESC' if source data are from FAEF Set to 'VSSTRESN' if source data are from VS
ASYMPINA Computation
Set to earlier date of: 1. Date of positive PCR test (MB.MBDTC) meets derivation of PARAM = 'Asymptomatic SARS-CoV-2 Infection per Adjudication' 2. Date of seroconversion due to infection (ADIS.ADT) where CRIT5FL = 'Y' and VISIT doesn't contain 'UNSCH' or 'ILLNESS' or 'CONVALESCENCE'
ASYMPINF Computation
Set to earlier date of: 1. Date of positive PCR test, ie, MB.MBDTC that meets derivation of PARAM = "Asymptomatic SARS-CoV-2 Infection"; 2. Date of seroconversion due to infection, ie, ADIS.ADT where CRIT5FL = "Y" and VISIT doesn't contain 'UNSCH' or 'ILLNESS' or 'CONVALESCENCE' in upper case.
COVID Computation
Set to the later date of the following two dates: 1. Date of positive PCR test (MB.MBDTC) meets derivation of PARAM = 'COVID-19' 2. Earliest date from following symptom date: Systemic symptoms: earliest ADSYMP.ADT of the 2nd eligible systemic symptom that occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date Respiratory symptom: earliest ADSYMP.ADT (use ADSYMP.ASTDT for PARAMCD in ('CEPNEU', 'REPNEU') and use ADSYMP.ADT when ADSYMP.ASTDT is missing) of the 1st eligible respiratory symptom that occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date
COVIDA Computation
Set to CE.CESDTC where CECAT='ADJUDICATION' and (CESCAT in ('COVID-19', 'SEVERE COVID-19'))
COVIDS Computation
Set to the later date of the following two dates: 1. Date of positive PCR test, ie, MB.MBDTC that meets derivation of PARAM = 'COVID-19 (Considering Scheduled RT-PCR)' 2. Earliest date from following symptom date: Systemic symptoms: earliest ADSYMP.ADT of the 2nd eligible systemic symptom that occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date Respiratory symptom: earliest ADSYMP.ADT (use ADSYMP.ASTDT for PARAMCD 'CEPNEU' and 'REPNEU' and use ADSYMP.ADT when ADSYMP.ASTDT is missing) of the 1st eligible respiratory symptom that occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date
COVIDSD Computation
Set to the later date of the following two dates: 1. Date of positive PCR test (MB.MBDTC) that meets derivation of PARAM = 'COVID-19 (Secondary Definition)' 2. Date of eligible symptom(s), defined as earliest ADSYMP.ADT of the 1st eligible symptom that occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date
COVIDSDS Computation
Set to the later date of the following two dates: 1. Date of positive PCR test (MB.MBDTC) that meets derivation of PARAM = 'COVID-19 (Secondary Definition and Considering Scheduled RT-PCR)' 2. Date of eligible symptom(s), defined as earliest ADSYMP.ADT of the 1st eligible symptom that occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date
COVIDSEV Computation
Set to the later date of the following dates: 1. ADT where PARAMCD = 'COVID' 2. Earliest date of first eligible severe symptom, defined as below: a. ADSYMP.ASTDT where ADSYMP.PARAMCD in ('RR30', 'HR125', 'OXYGEN93', 'PAO2F300', 'RF', 'ARDS', 'S90D60', 'VASOPRES', 'ARDYSF', 'HEPDYSF', 'NEURDYSF', 'ICU') with -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date. If ADSYMP.ASTDT is missing or < PCRDT-14 and ADSYMP.AENDT is within the window, use PCRDT-14 as the start date. Use ADSYMP.ADT when ADSYMP.ASTDT and ADSYMP.AENDT are missing b. ADSYMP.ADT where ADSYMP.PARAMCD = 'O2SAT93' with -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date c. ADSL.DTHDT if subject exists in AE with AE.AESDTH = 'Y' and SUPPAE.QNAM = 'AECVDIAG' and QVAL = 'Y' and ADSL.DTHDT within -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date
COVIDSVS Computation
Set to the later date of the following dates: 1. ADT where PARAMCD = 'COVIDS' 2. Earliest date of first eligible severe symptom, defined as below: a. ADSYMP.ASTDT where ADSYMP.PARAMCD in ('RR30', 'HR125', 'OXYGEN93', 'PAO2F300', 'RF', 'ARDS', 'S90D60', 'VASOPRES', 'ARDYSF', 'HEPDYSF', 'NEURDYSF', 'ICU') with -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date. If ADSYMP.ASTDT is missing or < PCRDT-14 and ADSYMP.AENDT is within the window, use PCRDT-14 as the start date. Use ADSYMP.ADT when ADSYMP.ASTDT and ADSYMP.AENDT are missing b. ADSYMP.ADT where ADSYMP.PARAMCD = 'O2SAT93' with -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date c. ADSL.DTHDT if subject exists in AE with AE.AESDTH = 'Y' and SUPPAE.QNAM = 'AECVDIAG' and QVAL = 'Y' and ADSL.DTHDT within -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date
DEATHCVD Computation
Set to ADSL.DTHDT due to COVID-19
INFECT Computation
Set to earlier date of: 1. Date of positive PCR test, ie, MB.MBDTC that meets derivation of PARAM = "SARS-CoV-2 Infection Regardless of Symptomatology or Severity". 2. Date of seroconversion due to infection, ie, ADIS.ADT where CRIT5FL = "Y".
ADY Computation
Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT + 1 if ADT is on or after ADSL.TR01SDT Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT if ADT is before ADSL.TR01SDT
ANL01FL Computation
Set to 'Y' for the record with AVALC = 'Y' and earliest ADT per PARAMCD
ASYMPINA Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'Asymptomatic SARS-CoV-2 Infection per Adjudication' and AVALC = 'Y' if no prior COVID-19 symptoms (no record created with PARAMCD='COVIDA' or 'COVIDSDS' and AVALC = 'Y' and ADT on/before the earlier date of 1 and 2) and at least one of the following criteria is met: 1. has positive RT-PCR test at Day 29 or participant decision visit (MB.MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2' and MB.MBSTRESC is in ('DETECTED', ‘POSITIVE') and VISIT = 'Visit 2 Day 29' or 'Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1') 2. has seroconversion due to infection (ADIS.CRIT5FL = 'Y' and VISIT doesn't contain 'UNSCH' or 'ILLNESS' or 'CONVALESCENCE')
ASYMPINF Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'Asymptomatic SARS-CoV-2 Infection' and AVALC = 'Y' if no prior COVID-19 symptoms (no record created with PARAMCD='COVIDS' or 'COVIDSDS' and AVALC = 'Y' and ADT on/before the earlier date of 1 and 2) and at least one of the following criteria is met: 1. has positive RT-PCR test at Day 29 or participant decision visit (ie, MB.MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2', MB.MBSTRESC is in ('DETECTED', 'POSITIVE') and VISIT in ('Visit 2 Day 29', 'Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1') 2. has seroconversion due to infection (ADIS.CRIT5FL = 'Y' and VISIT doesn't contain 'UNSCH' or 'ILLNESS' or 'CONVALESCENCE')
AVALC Computation
Set to 'Y'
AVISIT Computation
Only apply for PARAMCD in ('ASYMPINF, 'ASYMPINA'): 1. Use MB.VISIT of the RT-PCR result in below derivation if the case is derived based on positive RT-PCR only 2. Use ADIS.AVISIT of the seroconversion if the case is derived based on seroconversion only 3. Use MB.VISIT in below derivation if the case is derived based on both positive RT-PCR and seroconversion If ADY>1, Set to 'Day xx' part of VISIT for VISITNUM=6, 10, 15, 21, 32, Set to VISIT for VISIT = 'Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1', Set to 'Open Label Day 29' if VISIT = 'OL-D29', Set to 'Open Label Day 57' if VISIT = 'OL-D57', Set to null if other PARAMCD,
COVID Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'COVID-19' for each positive RT-PCR if following conditions are met: 1. RT-PCR is positive (MB.MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2' and MB.MBSTRESC is in ('DETECTED' or ‘POSITIVE’) after first dose (MB.MBDTC > ADSL.TR01SDT (non-missing)) and VISIT is not in ('Visit 2 Day 29', 'Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1') ) 2. if symptom(s) occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date (symptom event found from ADSYMP where ADSYMP.AVALC=Y and MB.MBDTC-14 <= ADSYMP.ADT <= MB.MBDTC+14): (a) at least two systemic symptom events found from ADSYMP where PARAMCD in ('FEVER', 'CHILLS', 'MYALGIA'/'BODYACHE', 'HEADACHE', 'STHROAT', 'NLSMELL'/'NLTASTE') where 'NLSMELL' and/or 'NLTASTE' are considered as one symptom, 'MYALGIA' and/or 'BODYACHE' are considered as one symptom, or (b) at least one respiratory symptom event found from ADSYMP where PARAMCD in ('COUGH', 'SHBREATH', 'DIBREATH', 'CEPNEU', 'REPNEU'). For 'CEPNEU' and 'REPNEU', use ADSYMP.ASTDT in place of ADSYMP.ADT and use ADSYMP.ADT when ADSYMP.ASTDT is missing
COVIDA Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'COVID-19 per Adjudication' if subject has SUPPCE.QVAL containing 'EVENT MEETS THE CHARTER DEFINITION OF COVID-19' where QNAM='CEREASOC'
COVIDS Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'COVID-19 (Considering Scheduled RT-PCR)' if following conditions are met: 1. RT-PCR is positive (MB.MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2', MB.MBSTRESC is in ('DETECTED', ‘POSITIVE) after first dose (MB.MBDTC > ADSL.TR01SDT (non-missing))) 2. if symptom(s) occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date (symptom event found from ADSYMP where ADSYMP.AVALC=Y and MB.MBDTC-14 <= ADSYMP.ADT <= MB.MBDTC+14): (a) at least two systemic symptom events found from ADSYMP where PARAMCD in ('FEVER', 'CHILLS', 'MYALGIA'/'BODYACHE', 'HEADACHE', 'STHROAT', 'NLSMELL'/'NLTASTE') where 'NLSMELL' and/or 'NLTASTE' are considered as one symptom, 'MYALGIA' and/or 'BODYACHE' are considered as one symptom, or (b) at least one respiratory symptom event found from ADSYMP where PARAMCD in ('COUGH', 'SHBREATH', 'DIBREATH', 'CEPNEU', 'REPNEU'). For 'CEPNEU' and 'REPNEU', use ADSYMP.ASTDT in place of ADSYMP.ADT and use ADSYMP.ADT when ADSYMP.ASTDT is missing
COVIDSD Computation
Create record for PARAM = 'COVID-19' for each RT-PCR is Positive (Secondary Definition)' if following conditions are met: 1. Select all subjects where RT-PCR is Positive (MB.MBSTRESC=DETECTED or POSITIVE due to prompt symptom) after First Dose (MBDTC>ADSL.TR01SDTC) and VISIT is not 'VISIT 2 Day 29' or 'Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1' 2. If a systemic symptom occurred within +/-14 days window of date with detected /positive as test result (a) any systemic symptom event found from ADSYMP where PARAMCD in ('FEVER', 'CHILLS', 'COUGH', 'SHBREATH', 'DIBREATH', 'FATIGUE', 'MYALGIA', 'BODYACHE', 'HEADACHE', 'NLTASTE', 'NLSMELL', 'STHROAT', 'NASALCON', 'RUNNOSE', 'NAUSEA', 'VOMIT', 'DIARRHEA')
COVIDSDS Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'COVID-19 (Secondary Definition and Considering Scheduled RT-PCR)' for each positive RT-PCR test after first dose if at least one systemic symptom occurred within +/-14 days window of positive PCR date: ADSYMP.PARAMCD in ('FEVER', 'CHILLS', 'COUGH', 'SHBREATH', 'DIBREATH', 'FATIGUE', 'MYALGIA', 'BODYACHE', 'HEADACHE', 'NLTASTE', 'NLSMELL', 'STHROAT', 'NASALCON', 'RUNNOSE', 'NAUSEA', 'VOMIT', 'DIARRHEA') and ADSYMP.AVALC=Y and MB.MBDTC-14 <= ADSYMP.ADT <= MB.MBDTC+14
COVIDSEV Computation
Create record for PARAM='Severe COVID-19' if following conditions are met: 1. Subject with PARAMCD='COVID', 2. At least one severe symptom (a) or (b) occurred within -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date (a) ADSYMP.PARAMCD in ('RR30', 'HR125', 'OXYGEN93', 'O2SAT93', 'PAO2F300', 'RF', 'ARDS', 'S90D60', 'VASOPRES', 'ARDYSF', 'HEPDYSF', 'NEURDYSF', 'ICU') and ADSYMP.AVALC='Y' and ((PCRDT-14 <= (ADT, ASTDT, or AENDT) <= PCRDT+28) or (ASTDT < PCRDT-14 and AENDT > PCRDT+28)), (b) AE.AESDTH = 'Y' and SUPPAE.QNAM = 'AECVDIAG' and QVAL = 'Y' and PCRDT-14 <= ADSL.DTHDT <= PCRDT+28
COVIDSVA Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'Severe COVID-19 per Adjudication' if subject has SUPPCE.QVAL containing 'EVENT MEETS THE CHARTER DEFINITION OF SEVERE COVID-19' where QNAM='CEREASOC'
COVIDSVS Computation
Create record for PARAM='Severe COVID-19 (Considering Scheduled RT-PCR)' if following conditions are met: 1. Subject with PARAMCD='COVIDS' and AVALC = 'Y' 2. At least one severe symptom occurred within -14/+28 days window of positive PCR date (a) ADSYMP.PARAMCD in ('RR30', 'HR125', 'OXYGEN93', 'PAO2F300', 'RF', 'ARDS', 'S90D60', 'VASOPRES', 'ARDYSF', 'HEPDYSF', 'NEURDYSF', 'ICU') and ADSYMP.AVALC='Y' and (PCRDT-14 <= ADSYMP.ASTDT<= PCRDT+28, or PCRDT-14 <= ADSYMP.AENDT<= PCRDT+28, or (ADSYMP.ASTDT < PCRDT-14 and ADSYMP.AENDT > PCRDT+28), use PCRDT-14 <= ADSYMP.ADT<= PCRDT+28 when ADSYMP.ASTDT and ADSYMP.AENDT are missing) (b) ADSYMP.PARAMCD = 'O2SAT93' and ADSYMP.AVALC='Y' and PCRDT-14 <= ADSYMP.ADT<= PCRDT+28 (c) AE.AESDTH = 'Y' and SUPPAE.QNAM = 'AECVDIAG' and QVAL = 'Y' and PCRDT-14 <= ADSL.DTHDT <= PCRDT+28
DEATHCVD Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'Death Caused by COVID-19' if subject has AE.AESDTH = 'Y' and SUPPAE.QNAM = 'AECVDIAG' and QVAL = 'Y' and ADSL.DTHDT is non-missing
EVIDINF Computation
For PARAMCD = 'INFECT', 'ASYMPINF', or 'ASYMPINA' Set to 'Virology' if the case is derived based on positive RT-PCR only, Set to 'Serology' if the case is derived based on seroconversion only, Set to 'Virology and Serology' if the case is derived based on both positive RT-PCR and seroconversion
INFECT Computation
Create a record for PARAM = 'SARS-CoV-2 Infection Regardless of Symptomatology or Severity' if at least one of the following criteria is met: 1. has seroconversion due to infection (ADIS.CRIT5FL = 'Y') 2. has positive RT-PCR test after first dose (MB.MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2', MB.MBSTRESC is in ('DETECTED', 'POSITIVE’) and MB.MBDTC > ADSL.TR01SDT (non-missing)
PARCAT1 Computation
Set to 'DERIVED PER ADJUDICATION' if PARAMCD in ('COVIDA', 'COVIDSVA', 'ASYMPINA'), otherwise, Set to 'DERIVED PER SAP'
PCRD29FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if the case is derived using positive RT-PCR at Day 29 ( MB.MBTESTCD = 'SARSCOV2', MB.MBSTRESC is in ('DETECTED' or 'POSITIVE' ), MB.VISIT = 'Visit 2 Day 29', and MB.MBDTC=PCRDT (non-missing)
PCRDT Computation
See derivation of PARAM. For PARAMCD = "COVID", "COVIDSD", "COVIDS", "COVIDSDS", set to the date of positive PCR test that meets derivation of corresponding PARAM; For PARAMCD = "COVIDSEV", set to the date of positive PCR test where PARAMCD = "COVID"; For PARAMCD = "COVIDSVS", set to the date of positive PCR test where PARAMCD = "COVIDS"; For PARAMCD = "INFECT", "ASYMPINF", or "ASYMPINA", set to null if PARAM is created based on seroconversion only (not based on positive RT-PCR), else set to the date of PCR test that meets derivation of corresponding PARAM; For PARAMCD = "DEATHCVD", set to the date of most recent post-baseline positive PCR if available (MB.MBDTC where MB.MBTESTCD="SARSCOV2", MB.MBSTRESC is "DETECTED" or "POSITIVE" in upper case, and MBDTC > ADSL.TR01SDT (non-missing)). Otherwise, null.
AENDT Computation
Converted date part of EX.EXENDTC to numeric
ASEQ Computation
Sort by USUBJID, VISIT, EX.EXSEQ, EX.ECSEQ and start from 1, increase by 1 for records within each subject
ASTDT Computation
Convert date part of EX.EXSTDTC to numeric
ASTDTM Computation
Convert EXSTDTC to numeric
DOSEYNFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if EXSTDTC is not missing. Set to 'N' if EXSTDTC is missing and EC.ECOCCUR='N'
NDOSERS Computation
Set to EC.ECREASOC
NDOSRSP Computation
Set to SUPPEC.QVAL where QNAM='EXREASSP'
NDOSRSP1 Computation
Set to SUPPEC.QVAL where QNAM='EXREASP1'
NDOSRSP2 Computation
Set to SUPPEC.QVAL where QNAM='EXREASP2'
SRCDOM Computation
Set to EX.DOMAIN if source data are from EX or Set to EC.DOMAIN if source data are from EC
SRCSEQ Computation
Set to EX.EXSEQ if source data are from EX or Set to EC.ECSEQ if source data are from EC
ABLFL Computation
Set to 'Y' for the latest (ADT) non-missing AVAL on or before ADSL.TR01SDT for each SUBJID, PARCAT1 and PARAMCD. Use ADT and TR01SDT if time is not available
ADT Computation
Convert date part of IS.ISDTC to numeric
ADTM Computation
Convert IS.ISDTC to numeric
ADY Computation
Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT if ADT is before ADSL.TR01SDT, otherwise, Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT + 1 if ADT is on or after ADSL.TR01SDT
ANL01FL Computation
If ABLFL='Y', then set to 'Y' For post-baseline assessments where AVISITN is non-missing and result (AVAL) is non-missing, per subject per parameter and per AVISIT: Within an AVISIT, set to ‘Y’ for the assessment at scheduled visit (i.e., VISIT doesn't contain "Unsched"). If there are 2 or more assessments at scheduled visit, set ‘Y’ to the latest assessment. If there are 2 or more assessments with non-missing AVAL on the latest assessment date, use the smaller AVAL, If there is no scheduled visit, set to 'Y' for the assessment closest to the target study day (record with minimum AWTDIFF) in the visit window. If there are 2 or more assessments equal distance to the target study day (AWTDIFFs are same), set to the latest assessment. If there are 2 or more assessments with non-missing AVAL on the latest assessment date, use the smaller AVAL
APERIOD Computation
Set to 2 if ADT>=AP02SDT>Missing, Otherwise, Set to 1
ATM Computation
Convert time part of IS.ISDTC to numeric
ATPT Computation
Set to 'Day x' If AVISIT='Illness Visit Day x' or 'Illness Visit y Day x' (See ADIS.AVISIT from Additional ADaM Variable Definition Doc). Otherwise, set to null

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

AVAL Computation
Set to LOG10(0.5* times ISLLOQ) if ISSTRESC contains '<' or 'BQL' or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ, Set to LOG10(ISULOQ) if ISSTRESC contains '>', Set to LOG10(IS.ISSTRESN), Otherwise
AVALC Computation
Set to IS.ISSTRESC if PARAMCD='SARSCOV2'
AVALO Computation
Set to 0.5 times ISLLOQ if ISSTRESC contains '<' or 'BQL' or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ, Set to ISULQ if ISSTRSC contains ">", Set to IS.ISSTRESN, Otherwise
AVALS Computation
Set to null
AVISIT Computation
See ADIS.AVISIT from Additional ADaM Variable Definition Doc.

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

AWTDIFF Computation
Set to absolute value of (ADY - AWTARGET)
BASE Computation
Set to AVAL where ABLFL = 'Y' for each SUBJID, PARCAT1 and PARAMCD
CHG Computation
Set to AVAL - BASE for post-baseline records
CRIT1 Computation
Set to '>=2-fold Increase from Baseline' if CRIT1FL='Y'
CRIT1FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if baseline result contains ('<', 'BQL') or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ, and post-baseline >= 2 x ISLLOQ (AVAL>=2 * ISLLOQ) or baseline result does not contains ('<' , 'BQL') and not <ISLLOQ and post-baseline increase 2 times from the baseline value (R2BASE>=2)
CRIT2 Computation
Set to '>=3-fold Increase from Baseline' if CRIT2FL='Y'
CRIT2FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if baseline result contains ('<', 'BQL') or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ, and post-baseline >= 2 x ISLLOQ (AVAL>=3 * ISLLOQ) or baseline result does not contain ('<' , 'BQL') and not <ISLLOQ and post-baseline increase 3 times from the baseline value (R2BASE>=3)
CRIT3 Computation
Set to '>=4-fold Increase from Baseline' if CRIT3FL='Y'
CRIT3FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if baseline result contains '<xxx' or ISSTRESN<ISLOD or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ, and post-baseline >= 4 x ISLLOQ (AVAL>=4 * ISLLOQ) or baseline result does not contain '<' and not <ISLOD and not <ISLLOQ and post-baseline increase 4 times from the baseline value (R2BASE>=4)
CRIT4 Computation
Set to 'Seroconversion Due to Vaccination' if CRIT4FL='Y'
CRIT4FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if baseline result ISSTRESC contains ('<', 'BQL') or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ and post-baseline >= ISLLOQ, or baseline result does not contain ('<' , 'BQL') and not < ISLLOQ and post-baseline increase 4 times from the baseline value (R2BASE>=4)
CRIT5 Computation
Set to 'Seroconversion Due to Infection if CRIT5FL='Y'
CRIT5FL Computation
For ADSL.ELECSBL= 'Negative': Set to 'Y' if PARAMCD='SARSCOV2' and post-baseline ISSTRESC='Positive' For ADSL.ELECSBL = 'Positive': Set to 'Y' if PARAMCD='V66IGGEN' and post-baseline result increased 4 times from the baseline (R2BASE>=4)
CRIT6 Computation
Set to 'Seroconversion' if CRIT6FL='Y'
CRIT6FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if baseline result contains ('<', 'BQL') or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ and post-baseline >= ISLLOQ (AVAL>=ISLLOQ) or baseline result does not contain ('<', 'BQL') and >= ISLLOQ and post-baseline increase x times from the baseline value (R2BASE>=x) where x=3.3 for PARAMCD='PSVNT50', x=2.3 for PARAMCD='PSVNT80', x=4.6 for PARAMCD='V65IGGS', x=1.9 for PARAMCD='S2PIGG', and x=4 for other PARAMCD
DTYPE Computation
Set to 'HALFLLOQ' if ISSTRESN<LLOQ or ISSTRESC contains '<' or 'BQL' Set to 'ULOQ' if ISSTRESC contains '>'
EUAVACFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if .< ADSL.EUAVACDT < ADT
ISLLOQ Computation
SUPPIS.QVAL where QNAM is 'ISLLOQ'
ISLOD Computation
Set to SUPPIS.QVAL where QNAM is 'ISLOD'
ISULOQ Computation
Set to SUPPIS.QVAL where QNAM is 'ISULOQ'
PARAM Computation
For PARCAT1='Serum SARS-CoV-2 Neutralizing Antibodies', Set to ISTEST For PARCAT1='Serum SARS-CoV-2 Binding Antibodies': Set to ISTEST " (" ||ISSTRESU|| ")" if PARAMCD does not contain 'L10' and ISSTRESU is non-missing, or ISTEST if ISSTRESU is not available for the test If PARAMCD contains 'L10' then assign PARAM based on PARAMCD: Set to 'LOG10(PsVNT50)' if PARAMCD='L10PVN50' Set to 'LOG10(PsVNT80)' if PARAMCD='L10PVN80' Set to 'LOG10(MN50)' if PARAMCD='L10MN50' Set to 'LOG10(VAC65 Spike IgG Antibody)' if PARAMCD='LV65IGGS' Set to 'LOG10(VAC66 Nucleocapsid IgG Antibody)' if PARAMCD='LV66IGGN' Set to 'LOG10(SARSCOV2S2P IgG Antibody)' if PARAMCD='LS2PIGG' Set to 'LOG10(SARSCOV2RBD IgG Antibody)' if PARAMCD='LRBDIGG' Set to 'LOG10(SARSCOV2NP IgG Antibody)' if PARAMCD='LNPIGG'.
PARAMCD Computation
Set to ISTESTCD and create follow PARAMCDs if AVAL is not missing and PARAM ne 'Elecsys SARS Cov-2 assay': L10PVN50, L10PVN80, L10MN50, LV65IGGS, LV66IGGN, LS2PIGG, LRBDIGG, LNPIGG
PARAMTYP Computation
Set to 'DERIVED' if PARAMCD contains 'L10' or 'LV58' or 'LV65' or 'LV66'
PARCAT1 Computation
Set to IS.ISCAT
PARCAT2 Computation
Set to 'Keep Actual Values Beyond ULOQ' if PARAMCD ne 'SARSCOV2'
R2BASE Computation
Set to AVAL/BASE if both are available and BASE is not 0 for post-baseline records and baseline result does not contain '<' or 'BQL' or ISSTRESN<ISLLOQ
RANGE Computation
Set to SUPPIS.QVAL where QNAM is 'RANGE'
TRTA Computation
If ADTM>TR01SDTM>. and (ADTM<=DOS2DTM or TR01SDTM is the last dose date time): Set to 'Placebo' if EX.EXTRT='PLACEBO' where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 1', Set to 'mRNA-1273' if EX.EXTRT='mRNA-1273' where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 1' If ADTM> ADSL.DOS2DTM>. and (ADTM<ADSL.TR02SDTM or ADSL.DOS2DTM is the last dose date time): Set to 'Placebo' if EX.EXTRT='PLACEBO' where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 29', Set to 'mRNA-1273' if EX.EXTRT='mRNA-1273' where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 29' If ADTM >ADSL.TR02SDTM>. and (ADTM<ADSL.OLDO2DTM or TR02SDTM is the last dose date time): Set to 'Placebo' if EX.EXTRT='PLACEBO' where EX.VISIT contains 'OL-D1', Set to 'mRNA-1273' if EX.EXTRT='mRNA-1273' where EX.VISIT contains 'OL-D1' If .<ADSL.OLDO2DTM<=ADTM: Set to 'Placebo' if EX.EXTRT='PLACEBO' where EX.VISIT contains 'OL-D29', Set to 'mRNA-1273' if EX.EXTRT='mRNA-1273' where EX.VISIT contains 'OL-D29' Note: If time part of ADTM, TR01SDTM, DOS2DTM, TR02SDTM, or OLDO2DTM is missing, use ADT, TR01SDT, DOSE2DT, TR02SDT, and OLDOS2DT to replace ADTM, TR01SDTM, DOS2DTM, TR02SDTM, and OLDO2DTM, respectively
ABLFL Computation
Set to 'Y' for last ADT on or before ADSL.TR01SDT with AVALC = 'Negative'/'Positive' for each SUBJID, PARCAT1 and PARAMCD. If there are multiple tests on the same date, select AVALC in the order of Positive > Negative
ADT Computation
Convert date part of MB.MBDTC to numeric
ADTM Computation
Convert MB.MBDTC to numeric
ADY Computation
Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT if ADT is before ADSL.TR01SDT Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT + 1 if ADT is on or after ADSL.TR01SDT
ANL01FL Computation
See ADMB.ANL01FL from Additional ADaM Variable Difinition Doc

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

ATM Computation
Convert time part of MB.MBDTC to numeric
ATPT Computation
Set to MB.MBTPT if MB.MBTPT is not missing or Set ATPT='Day x' if original AVISIT='Illness Visit Day x' or 'Illness Visit y Day x'
AVALC Computation
Set to 'Negative' if upcase(MBSTRESC) is 'NOT DETECTED' or 'NEGATIVE' or Set to 'Positive' if upcase(MBSTRESC) is 'DETECTED' or 'POSITIVE' Set to MBSTRESC, Otherwise
AVISIT Computation
See ADMB.AVISIT from Additional ADaM Variable Difinition Doc.

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

AWRANGE Computation
See ADMB.AWRANGE from Additional ADaM Variable Difinition Doc.

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

AWTARGET Computation
See ADMB.AWTARGET from Additional ADaM Variable Difinition Doc.

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

AWTDIFF Computation
Set to absolute value of (ADY - AWTARGET)
BASEC Computation
Set to AVALC where ABLFL = 'Y' for each SUBJID, PARCAT1 and PARAMCD
LDTCLIA Computation
Set to SUPPMB.QVAL where QNAM is 'LDTCLIA'
LOCALFL Computation
Set to SUPPMB.QVAL where QNAM is 'LOCALFL'
PARAM Computation
Set to MB.MBTEST
PARAMCD Computation
Set to MB.MBTESTCD
PARCAT1 Computation
Set to MB.MBCAT
CQ01FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if CQ01NAM is not missing
CQ01NAM Computation
Set to 'Autoimmune' if MHDECOD is in import.CMQ where CMQNAME='AUTOIMMUNE'
CQ02FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if CQ02NAM is not missing
CQ02NAM Computation
Set to 'Dermal Filler Reaction Post Vaccination' if MHDECOD is in import.CMQ where CMQNAME='DERMAL FILLER REACTION POST VACCINATION'
SMQ01FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if SMQ01NAM is not missing
SMQ01NAM Computation
Set to 'Anaphylactic Reaction' if AEDECOD is in import.SMQ where SMQNAME='ANAPHYLACTIC REACTION'
SMQ01SC Computation
Set to SMQ.SCOPE if AEDECOD is in import.SMQ where SMQNAME='ANAPHYLACTIC REACTION'
SMQ02FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if SMQ02NAM is not missing and SMQ02SC is 'Narrow'
SMQ02NAM Computation
Set to 'Angioedema' if MHDECOD is in import.SMQ where SMQNAME='ANGIOEDEMA'
SMQ02SC Computation
Set to SMQ.SCOPE if MHDECOD is in import.SMQ where SMQNAME='ANGIOEDEMA'
SMQ06FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if SMQ06NAM is not missing and SMQ06SC is 'Narrow'
SMQ06NAM Computation
Set to 'Hypersensitivity' if AEDECOD is in import.SMQ where SMQNAME='HYPERSENSITIVITY'
SMQ06SC Computation
Set to SMQ.SCOPE if AEDECOD is in import.SMQ where SMQNAME='HYPERSENSITIVITY'
AVALC Computation
For PARAMCD='OTHERLOC' or 'OTHEROCC', set to 'N' if SC.SCSTRESC='N', else set to 'Y' if SCSTRESC is not missing. For other PARAMCD, set to SC.SCSTRESC.
OTHSPY Computation
If PARAMCD='OTHEROCC' or 'OTHERLOC', set to SCSTRESC. Otherwise, set to null.
PARAM Computation
Set to mixed case of SC.SCTEST if SC.SCTEST not in ('Other', 'High density housing', 'Low density, multi-family setting', 'Multi-family dwelling', 'Nursing Home or Assisted Living Facility', 'Single family home') or Set to 'Resides in High Density Housing' if SC.SCTEST='High density housing' or Set to 'Resides in Low Density, Multi-Family Setting' if SC.SCTEST='Low density, multi-family setting' or Set to 'Resides in Multi-Family Dwelling'if SC.SCTEST='Multi-family dwelling' or Set to 'Resides in Nursing Home or Assisted Living Facility' if SC.SCTEST='Nursing Home or Assisted Living Facility' or Set to 'Resides in a Single Family Home' if SC.SCTEST='Single family home' or Set to 'Other Occupational Risk' if SC.SCTEST='Other' and PARCAT1='OCCUPATIONAL RISK' or Set to 'Other Location And Living Circumstances Risk' if SC.SCTEST='Other' and PARCAT1='LOCATION AND LIVING CIRCUMSTANCES RISK'
PARCAT1 Computation
Set to SC.SCSCAT
AGEGR1 Computation
Set to '>=18 and <65 Years' if 18<=AGE<65 Set to '>=65 Years' if AGE >=65
AGEGR1 Computation
Based on AGEGR1: Set to 1 if AGEGR1 is '>=18 and <65 Years' Set to 2 if AGEGR1 is '>=65 Years'
AGEGR2 Computation
Set to '>=18 and <65 Years' if 18 <= AGE < 65 Set to '>=65 and <75 Years' if 65 <= AGE < 75 Set to '>=75 if AGE >= 75 Years'
AGEGR2N Computation
Base on AGEGR2: Set to 1 if AGEGR2 is '>=18 and <65 Years' Set to 2 if AGEGR2 is '>=65 and <75 Years' Set to 3 if AGEGR2 is '>=75 Years'
AGEGR3 Computation
Set to '>=18 and <65 Years' if non-missing AGE<65, Set to '>=65 and <75 Years' if 65 <= AGE < 75, Set to '>=75 and <85 Years' if 75 <= AGE < 85, Set to '>=85 Years' if AGE >= 85
AGEGR3N Computation
Set to 1 if AGEGR2 is '>=18 and <65 Years', Set to 2 if AGEGR2 is '>=65 and <75 Years', Set to 3 if AGEGR2 is '>=75 and <85 Years', Set to 4 if AGEGR2 is '>=85 Years'
AGEGR4 Computation
Set to '>=18 and <=25 Years' if 18 <=AGE<=25, Set to '>=26 and <=50 Years' if 26 <= AGE <= 50
AGEGR4N Computation
Set to 1 if AGEGR4 is '>=18 and <=25 Years', Set to 2 if AGEGR4 is '>=26 and <=50 Years'
AP01EDT Computation
Set to AP02SDT-1 if AP02SDT is not missing, Set to the earlier date of EOSDT and DTHDT
AP01SDT Computation
Set to RANDDT
AP01SEDT Computation
Set to AP02SSDT-1 if AP02SSDT is not missing, Set to the earlier date of EOSDT and DTHDT
AP01SSDT Computation
Set to RANDDT
AP02EDT Computation
Set to the earlier date of EOSDT and DTHDT if AP02SDT is not missing
AP02SDT Computation
Set to PDVDT, UBLDDT, or IRTVISDT, whichever is the earliest date after TR01EDT. If AP02SDT is after EOSDT or DTHDT then set AP02SDT as missing.
AP02SEDT Computation
Set to the earlier date of EOSDT and DTHDT if AP02SSDT is not missing
AP02SSDT Computation
Set to TR02SDT if not missing, Set to PDVDT, UBLDDT, or IRTVISDT, whichever is earlier
BMIBL Computation
Set to WEIGHTBL/(HEIGHTBL in meters)^2
CBNRS Computation
Set to SUPPRP.QVAL where QNAM='CBRSN' and VISIT='Screening'
CCIASFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if RANDFL='Y' and subject is in the ccIAS Cohort sampling list. Set to 'N', otherwise Note: Use latest ccias_unblinded dataset. Subject eligibilities for sampling are specified in Immune sampling plan
CHILDBP Computation
Set to RP.RPORRES where RPTESTCD is CHILDPOT and VISIT='Screening'
COMPLFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if USUBJID exists in DS where DSCAT = 'DISPOSITION EVENT' and DS.DSSCAT = 'END OF STUDY' and DSDECOD = 'COMPLETED' Set to 'N' if USUBJID exists in DS where DSCAT = 'DISPOSITION EVENT' and DS.DSSCAT = 'END OF STUDY' and DSDECOD <> 'COMPLETED'
COVIDAFL Computation
Set to 'Y' where SUPPCE.QNAM='CEREASOC' and SUPPCE.QVAL containing 'EVENT MEETS THE CHARTER DEFINITION OF COVID-19' and CE.CESTDTC<=EFFCODT, Set to 'N', otherwise
CUTOFFDT Computation
Set to TS.TSVAL where TS.TSPARMCD='DCUTDTC'
CVDSVAFL Computation
Set to 'Y' where SUPPCE.QNAM='CEREASOC' and SUPPCE.QVAL containing 'EVENT MEETS THE CHARTER DEFINITION OF SEVERE COVID-19' and CE.CESTDTC<=EFFCODT, Set to 'N', otherwise
DCSREAS Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='END OF STUDY' AND DSDECOD not in ('COMPLETED', 'ADVERSE EVENT', 'SAE', 'PHYSICIAN DESICION', 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', 'OTHER', 'DEATH') Set to 'Adverse Event' if DS.DSDECOD is 'ADVERSE EVENT' Set to 'Serious Adverse Event' if DS.DSDECOD is 'SAE' Set to 'Protocol Deviation' if DS.DSDECOD is 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION' Set to 'Other' if DS.DSDECOD is 'OTHER' Set to 'Physician Decision' if DS.DSDECOD is 'PHYSICIAN DESICION' Set to 'Withdrawal of Consent by Participant' if DS.DSDECOD is 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT' Set to 'Death' if DS.DSDECOD='DEATH'
DCSREASP Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='END OF STUDY' AND DSDECOD in ('ADVERSE EVENT', 'SAE', 'PHYSICIAN DESICION', 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', 'OTHER') and DSTERM^=DSDECOD
DCT01RS Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and EPOCH='BLINDED TREATMENT' AND DSDECOD not in ('COMPLETED', 'ADVERSE EVENT', 'SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENT', 'PHYSICIAN DECISION', 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', 'OTHER', 'DEATH', 'COVID'), Set to 'Adverse Event' if DS.DSDECOD is 'ADVERSE EVENT', Set to 'Serious Adverse Event' if DS.DSDECOD is 'SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENT', Set to 'Protocol Deviation' if DS.DSDECOD is 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', Set to 'Other' if DS.DSDECOD is 'OTHER', Set to 'Physician Decision' if DS.DSDECOD is 'PHYSICIAN DECISION', Set to 'Withdrawal of Consent by Participant' if DS.DSDECOD is 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', Set ot 'Death' if DS.DSDECOD='DEATH', Set to 'Due to SARS-CoV-2' if DS.DSDECOD='COVID', Set to 'Death' if DS.DSDECOD='DEATH' Set to 'Discontinuation from Study' if EOT01STT='DISCONTINUED' and COMPLFL='N' and no above mentioned record in DS
DCT01RSP Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and EPOCH='BLINDED TREATMENT' AND DSDECOD in ('ADVERSE EVENT', 'SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENT', 'PHYSICIAN DECISION', 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', 'OTHER')
DCT02RS Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where DS.DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DS.DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and DS.EPOCH='OPEN LABEL TREATMENT' and DS.DSDECOD not in ('COMPLETED', 'ADVERSE EVENT', 'SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENT', 'PHYSICIAN DECISION', 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', 'OTHER', 'DEATH', 'COVID'), Set to 'Adverse Event' if DS.DSDECOD is 'ADVERSE EVENT', Set to 'Serious Adverse Event' if DS.DSDECOD is 'SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENT', Set to 'Protocol Deviation' if DS.DSDECOD is 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', Set to 'Other' if DS.DSDECOD is 'OTHER', Set to 'Physician Decision' if DS.DSDECOD is 'PHYSICIAN DESICION', Set to 'Withdrawal of Consent by Participant' if DS.DSDECOD is 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', Set to 'Death' if DS.DSDECOD='DEATH', Set to 'Due to SARS-CoV-2' if DS.DSDECOD='COVID', Set to 'Discontinuation from Study' if EOT02STT='DISCONTINUED' and COMPLFL='N' and no above mentioned record in DS
DCT02RSP Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where DS.DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DS.DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and DS.EPOCH='OPEN LABEL TREATMENT' AND DS.DSDECOD in ('ADVERSE EVENT', 'SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENT', 'PHYSICIAN DECISION', 'WITHDRAWAL BY SUBJECT', 'PROTOCOL DEVIATION', 'OTHER')
DOS2DTM Computation
Convert EX.EXSTDTC to numeric where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 29' and EX.EXSTDTC is non-missing
DOSE1FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if USUBJID exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 1' Set to 'N', otherwise
DOSE2DT Computation
Convert date part of EX.EXSTDTC to numeric where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 29' and EX.EXSTDTC is non-missing
DOSE2FL Computation
Set 'Y' if USUBJID exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT contains 'Day 29' Set to 'N' otherwise
DSDTHSP Computation
Set to SUPPDD.QVAL where SUPPDD.QNAM='DSDTHSP'
DTHAUTOP Computation
Set to DD.DDORRES where DDTESTCD='AUTOPERF'
DTHCAUS Computation
Set to DD.DDORRES where DDTESTCD='DTHCAUS'
DTHDT Computation
Convert DD.DDDTC to numeric or Convert AEENDTC where AE.AESDTH='Y' to numeric if DD.DDDTC is missing
EFFCODT Computation
Set to CUTOFFDT or EUAVACDT, whichever is the earliest date after TR01EDT.
ELECSBL Computation
Set to 'Positive' if USUBJID exists in IS with ISTESTCD='SARSCOV2', ISORRES='Positive' and non-missing ISDTC<=TR01SDT Set to 'Negative' if USUBJID exists with ISTESTCD='SARSCOV2', ISORRES='Negative' and non-missing ISDTC<=TR01SDT, Otherwise, Set to null. Note: Use last (only consider date part) non-missing results on/before TR01SDT for derivation
EOSDT Computation
Convert DS.DSSTDTC where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='END OF STUDY' to numeric
EOSDY Computation
Set to EOSDT-TR01SDT+1 if SAFFL='Y' and EOSDT>=TR01SDT Set to EOSDT-RANDDT+1 if RANDFL='Y' and EOSDT>=RANDDT Set to missing, otherwise
EOSSTT Computation
If RANDFL='Y': Set to 'COMPLETED' if COMPLFL='Y' Set to 'DISCONTINUED' if COMPLFL='N' Set to 'ONGOING' If RANDFL='N' then Set to null
EOT01DT Computation
Convert DS.DSSTDTC where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and EPOCH='BLINDED TREATMENT' to numeric, set to DOSE2DT if EOT01STT is 'COMPLETED'
EOT01DY Computation
Set to EOT01DT-TR01SDT+1 if EOT01DT>=TR01SDT
EOT01STT Computation
Set to 'COMPLETED' if DOSE2FL='Y', Set to 'DISCONTINUED' if USUBJID exists in DS where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and DSDECOD^='COMPLETED' and EPOCH='BLINDED TREATMENT'
EOT02DT Computation
Covert DS.DSSTDTC where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' and EPOCH='OPEN LABEL TREATMENT' or 'FOLLOW-UP OPEN LABEL PHASE' to numeric Set to OLDOS2DT if EOT02STT is 'COMPLETED' and (OLDOS2FL='Y' and TRT01AN^=2), or set to TR02EDT if (OLDOS1FL='Y' and TRT01AN=2)
EOT02DY Computation
EOT02DT-TR02SDT+1 if EOT02DT>=TR02SDT
EOT02STT Computation
Set to 'COMPLETED' if (OLDOS2FL='Y' and TRT01AN^=2) or (OLDOS1FL='Y' and TRT01AN=2), Set to 'DISCONTINUED' if USUBJID exists in DS where DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='STUDY TREATMENT' AND DSDECOD^='COMPLETED' and EPOCH='OPEN LABEL TREATMENT ', Set to 'ONGOING' if (TRT02PN=2 and OLDOS1FL^='Y' and OLDOS2FL^='Y') or (TRT01AN^=2 and TRT02PN=2 and OLDOS2FL^='Y')
EUAVACDT Computation
See ADSL.EUAVACDT from ADaM-Variable-Definition.pdf

Additional ADaM Variable Definition

FASEREAS Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y' 1. Set to 'Did not receive any vaccination' if there is no record exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC 2. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' if there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis' or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing), After above steps, if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-2, then concatenate reason with ',' Set to null, otherwise
FASFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if all criteria met: 1. RANDFL='Y', 2. USUBJID exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC, 3. There is no record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets', or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and (DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT and AP01EDT is not missing or DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT if AP01ENDT is missing) Set to 'N', otherwise
HEIGHTBL Computation
Set to the last non-missing VS.VSSTRESN where VSTESTCD = “HEIGHT” and (VSDTC is before the first vaccination (DM.RFXSTDTC) or on the first vaccination date with VSTPT contains 'PRE-DOSE'), if missing use non-missing VS.VSSTRESN where VSTESTCD='HEIGHT' and or VISIT='Screening' with VSTPT^='POST-DOSE'
IRTVISDT Computation
Convert date part of SUPPDS.QVAL where QNAM = 'IRTVISDT' to numeric
MINORITY Computation
Only for subjects with (RACE is not missing or not equal to ‘NOT REPORTED’ or ‘UNKNOWN’ ) or (ETHNIC is not missing or not equal to ‘NOT REPORTED’ or ‘UNKNOWN’ ): Set to 'Minority' if ADSL.RACE is equal to ''AMERICAN INDIAN OR ALASKA NATIVE', 'BLACK OR AFRICAN AMERICAN', 'NATIVE HAWAIIAN OR OTHER PACIFIC ISLANDER', or ADSL.ETHNIC= ‘HISPANIC OR LATINO’, Set to 'Non-minority', otherwise
MITTERS Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y'. 1. Set to 'Did not receive any vaccination' if there is no record exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC, 2. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' If there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis' or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing), 3. Set to 'PCR and/or serology positive at baseline' if SCOV2BL='Positive', 4. Set to 'PCR and/or serology missing at baseline' if SCOV2BL='', After above steps, if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-4, then concatenate reason with ',' Set to null, otherwise
MITTFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if FASFL='Y' and SCOV2BL = 'Negative' Set to 'N', otherwise
OLDO2DTM Computation
Convert non-missing EX.EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT='OL-D29' to numeric.
OLDOS1FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if USUBJID exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT contains 'OL-D1', Set to 'N', otherwise
OLDOS2DT Computation
Convert date part of non-missing EX.EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT='OL-D29' to numeric
OLDOS2FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if USUBJID exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT contains 'OL-D29', Set to 'N', otherwise
PDVDT Computation
Convert date part of SV.SVSTDTC where VISIT='Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1'
PPEREAS Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y' 1. Set to 'Excluded from mITT population' if MITTFL='N', 2. Set to 'Did not receive Vaccination #2 per schedule' if DOSE2FL='N' 3. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' if there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets' or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '3 - Exclude from per-protocol analysis set only' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing) 4. Set to 'Received incorrect vaccination' if there is any record in EX where EXTRT (non-missing) ne TRT01P in any case, 5. Set to 'Received Vaccination #2 out of window' if DOSE2FL='Y' and (non-missing DOSE2DT - TR01SDT < 21 or > 42), After above steps, if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-5, then concatenate reason with ',' Set to null otherwise
PPROTFL Computation
Set 'Y' if all criteria met: 1. MITTFL='Y', 2. DOSE2FL='Y' and 21 <= DOSE2DT - TR01SDT <= 42, 3. There is no record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets' or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '3 - Exclude from per-protocol analysis set only' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and (DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT if AP01EDT is not missing or DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT if AP01EDT is missing), 4. There is no record in EX where EXTRT (non-missing) ne TRT01P in any case Set to 'N', otherwise
PPSIEREA Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y': 1. Set to 'Not in random subcohort for immunogenicity' if RANDIGFL='N', 2. Set to 'Did not receive Vaccination #2 per schedule' if DOSE2FL='N', 3. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' if there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets' or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '3 - Exclude from per-protocol analysis set only' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing), 4. Set to 'Received incorrect vaccination in blinded phase' if there is any dosing error in blinded phase - can find record where iEXTRT (non-missing) ne TRT01P and VISIT in ('Visit 1 Day 1' 'Visit 2 Day 29') and in any case, 5. Set to 'Received Vaccination #2 out of window' if DOSE2FL='Y' and (non-missing DOSE2DT - TR01SDT < 21 or > 42), 6. Set to 'Human Immunodeficiency Virus Infection' if RSKF6 is not missing, Concatenate reason with ',' if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-6
PPSIFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if all criteria met: 1. RANDIGFL='Y', 2. DOSE2FL='Y' and 21 <= DOSE2DT - TR01SDT <= 42, 3. There is no record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets' or '2 - Exclude from all efficacy analysis (full analysis set and per-protocol analysis set)' or '3 - Exclude from per-protocol analysis set only' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and (DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT if AP01EDT is not missing or DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT if AP01EDT is missing), 4. There is no records found in EX where EXTRT not missing and EXTRT ne TRT01P in any case, 5. RSKF6 is missing Set to 'N', otherwise
PREVSCR Computation
Set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM='PREVSCR' per USUBJID
PROTVER Computation
Set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM is PROTVER
RACEGR1 Computation
Set to 'Caucasian' if RACE='WHITE' Set to 'Non-caucasian' if RACE is not missing or not equal to ‘NOT REPORTED’ or ‘UNKNOWN’
RACEGR1N Computation
Based on RACEGR1: Set to 1 if RACEGR1='Caucasian' Set to 2 if RACEGR1 is 'Non-caucasian'
RACESPY Computation
Set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM is RACEOTH if RACE='OTHER', Concatenate SUPPDM.QVAL with ', ' where QNAM is among RACE1 - RACE6 if RACE='MULTIPLE'
RANDDT Computation
Set to DS.DSSTDTC where DSTERM='RANDOMIZED' and DSCAT='PROTOCOL MILESTONE'
RANDFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if both criteria met: 1. USUBJID exists in DS where DSDECOD='RANDOMIZED' and DSSTDTC not missing and DSREFID not missing 2. there is no record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets' and DVSTDTC <= AP02SDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP02SDT applies only when AP02SDT is not missing) Set to 'N', otherwise
RANDIGFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if subject is randomized to the ccIAS cohort sampling list (RANDSFL='Y' in ccias_unblinded dataset), Set to 'N', otherwise Note: Use latest ccias_unblinded dataset. Subject eligibilities for sampling are specified in Immune sampling plan
RANDNUM Computation
Set to DS.DSREFID
RETHGR1 Computation
Only for subjects with (non-missing RACE not equal to ‘NOT REPORTED’ or ‘UNKNOWN’) or (non-missing ETHNIC not equal to ‘NOT REPORTED’ or ‘UNKNOWN’): Set to 'White' if RACE='WHITE' and ETHNIC ne 'HISPANIC OR LATINO' Set to 'Community of Colors', otherwise
RETHGR1N Computation
Based on RETHGR1 Set to 1 if RETHGR1='White' Set to 2 if RETHGR1='Communities of Color'
RFICDT Computation
Set to date part of DM.RFICDTC in numeric format
RISKGR1 Computation
Only derived for subjects where RANDFL='Y': Set to 'At Risk' if at least one of RSKF1-RSK6 in not missing, otherwise Set to 'Not At Risk'
RISKGR1N Computation
Based on RISKGR1: Set to 1 if RISKGR1='At Risk' Set to 2 if RISKGR1='Not At Risk'
RSKF1 Computation
Set to 'Chronic Lung Disease' if exist record in MH where MHTERM='LUNG DISEASE' and MHOCCUR='Y' and MHCAT='RISK FACTOR FOR COVID-19'
RSKF2 Computation
Set to 'Significant Cardiac Disease' if exist record in MH where MHTERM='CARDIAC DISEASE' and MHOCCUR='Y' and MHCAT='RISK FACTOR FOR COVID-19'
RSKF3 Computation
Set to 'Severe Obesity' if exist record in MH where MHTERM='SEVERE OBESITY' and MHOCCUR='Y' and MHCAT='RISK FACTOR FOR COVID-19'
RSKF4 Computation
Set to 'Diabetes' if exist record in MH where MHTERM='DIABETES' and MHOCCUR='Y' and MHCAT='RISK FACTOR FOR COVID-19'
RSKF5 Computation
Set to 'Liver Disease' if exist record in MH where MHTERM='LIVER DISEASE' and MHOCCUR='Y' and MHCAT='RISK FACTOR FOR COVID-19'
RSKF6 Computation
Set to 'Human Immunodeficiency Virus Infection' if exist record in MH where MHTERM='HIV' and MHOCCUR='Y' and MHCAT='RISK FACTOR FOR COVID-19'
RTPCRBL Computation
Set to 'Positive' if USUBJID exists in MB with MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2' and SUPPMB.QVAL is not 'Y' where QNAM is 'LOCALFL' and MBSTRESC='Detected' and date part of non-missing MBDTC<=TR01SDT, otherwise Set to 'Negative' if USUBJID exists MB with MBTESTCD='SARSCOV2' and SUPPMB.QVAL is not 'Y' where QNAM is 'LOCALFL' and MBSTRESC='Not Detected' and date part of non-missing MBDTC<=TR01SDT Note: Use last (only consider date part) non-missing results on/before TR01SDT for derivation
SAFEREAS Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y' 1. Set to 'Did not receive any vaccination' if there is no record exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC, 2. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' if there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing), After above steps, if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-2, then concatenate reason with ',' Set to Null, otherwise
SAFFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if all criteria met: 1. RANDFL='Y', 2. USUBJID exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC, 3. There is no record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis sets', or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and (DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT and AP01EDT is not missing or DVSTDTC <= EFFCODT if AP01ENDT is missing) Set to 'N', otherwise
SAR1ERS Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y' 1. Set to 'Did not receive Vaccination' if there is no record exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC, 2. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' If there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing), 3. Set to 'Did not contribute any solicited AR data for Vaccination #1' if SAFFL='Y' and SAR1FL='N', After above steps, if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-3, then concatenate reason with ',' Set to null, otherwise
SAR1FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if both criteria met: 1. SAFFL='Y' 2. Have at least one non-missing FAORRES where FATPTREF = 'DOSE 1' in FACE OR have at least one non-missing VSORRES where VSTPTREF = 'DOSE 1' and VSTEST contains "Temperature" where VSCAT contains "REACTOGENICITY" in VS Set to 'N', otherwise
SAR2ERS Computation
Only for subjects with RANDFL='Y' 1. Set to 'Did not receive Vaccination' if there is no record exists in EX with non-missing EXSTDTC, 2. Set to 'Had major protocol deviations' if there is at least one record where SUPPDV.QNAM ='SEVDES' and SUPPDV.QVAL is '1 - Exclude from all analysis' or '8 - Exclude from all analysis sets except for randomization set' and DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT (condition of DVSTDTC <= AP01EDT applies only when AP01EDT is not missing), 3. Set to 'Did not receive Vaccination' if SAFFL='Y' and DOSE2FL='N', 4. Set to 'Did not contribute any solicited AR data for Vaccination #2' if SAFFL='Y' and DOSE2FL='Y' and SAR2FL='N', After above steps, if a subject satisfies more than one of 1-4, then concatenate reason with ',' Set to Null, otherwise
SAR2FL Computation
Set to 'Y' if all criteria met: 1. SAFFL='Y' 2. Have at least one non-missing FAORRES where FATPTREF = 'DOSE 2' in FACE OR have at least one non-missing VSORRES where VSTPTREF = 'DOSE 2' and VSTEST contains 'Temperature' where VSCAT contains 'REACTOGENICITY' in VS 3. DOSE2FL='Y' Set to 'N', otherwise
SARAFL Computation
Set to 'Y' if SAR1FL='Y' or SAR2FL='Y' Set to 'N', otherwise
SCOV2BL Computation
Set to 'Positive' if RTPCRBL='Positive' or ELECSBL='Positive' Set to 'Negative' if RTPCRBL='Negative' and ELECSBL='Negative'
CBNRS Computation
Set to SUPPRP.QVAL where QNAM='CBRSN' and VISIT='Screening'
CHILDBP Computation
Set to RP.RPORRES where RPTESTCD is CHILDPOTand VISIT=Screening
PREVSCR Computation
Set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM='PREVSCR' per USUBJID
PROTVER Computation
Set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM is PROTVER and VISIT = Screening
RACESPY Computation
If RACE='OTHER' then set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM is RACEOTH, If RACE='MULTIPLE' then concatenate mixed case of QVAL with ', ' where QNAM is among RACE1 - RACE6
RFICDT Computation
Convert date part of DM.RFICDTC
SCFREAS Computation
Mixed case of DS.DSTERM where DSCAT = 'DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT='SCREEN FAILURE' and DS.DSDECOD ^= 'OTHER'. Set to 'Other' if DS.DSDECOD = 'OTHER' where DSCAT = 'DISPOSITION EVENT' and DSSCAT = 'SCREEN FAILURE'
SCFREASP Computation
Set to DS.DSTERM where SCFREAS='Other'
STRATAR Computation
Set to SUPPDM.QVAL where QNAM='COHORT'
STRATARN Computation
Based on 'STRATAR': Set to 1 if '>=18 and <65 Years and Not at Risk' Set to 2 if '>=18 and <65 Years and at Risk' Set to 3 if '>=65 Years'
STRATAV Computation
Set to '>=18 and <65 Years and Not at Risk' if AGEGR1N=1 and all of RSKF1--RSKF6 are missing Set to '>=18 and <65 Years and at Risk' if AGEGR1N=1 and at least one of RSKF1--RSKF6 is not missing Set to '>=65 Years' if AGEGR1N=2
STRATAVN Computation
Based on 'STRATAV': Set to 1 if '>=18 and <65 Years and Not at Risk' Set to 2 if '>=18 and <65 Years and at Risk' Set to 3 if '>=65 Years'
STUDDUR1 Computation
Derived for subjects with SAFFL='Y': Set to EOSDT-RANDDT+1 if EOSDT not missing Set to CUTOFFDT-RANDDT+1 if EOSDT missing and EOSSTT='ONGOING'
STUDDUR2 Computation
Derived for subjects with SAFFL='Y': Set to EOSDT-TR01SDT+1 if EOSDT not missing set to CUTOFFDT-TR01SDT+1 if EOSDT missing and EOSSTT='ONGOING'
STUDDUR3 Computation
Derived for subjects with SAFFL='Y': Set to EOSDT-DOSE2DT+1 if DOSE2FL='Y' and EOSDT not missing Set to CUTOFFDT-DOSE2DT+1 if DOSE2FL='Y' and EOSDT missing and EOSSTT='ONGOING' Set to 0 if DOSE2FL='N'
STUDDUR4 Computation
DOSE2DT - TR01SDT
STUDDUR5 Computation
AP02SDT - RANDDT + 1, Note: Use EOSDT if AP02SDT is missing, Use CUTOFFDT if EOSDT is also missing
STUDDUR6 Computation
Derive for subjects with AP02SDT not missing: EOSDT - AP02SDT + 1, Note: Use CUTOFFDT if EOSDT is missing
TR01EDT Computation
Convert date part of the latest non-missing EX.EXENDTC where VISIT in ('Visit 1 Day 1', 'Visit 2 Day 29') to numeric
TR01EDTM Computation
Convert the latest non-missing EX.EXENDTC where VISIT in ('Visit 1 Day 1', 'Visit 2 Day 29') to numeric
TR01SDT Computation
Convert date part of DM.RFXSTDTC to numeric
TR01SDTM Computation
Convert DM.RFXSTDTC to numeric
TR02EDT Computation
Convert date part of latest non-missing EX.EXENDTC where VISIT in ('Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1', 'OL-D29') to numeric
TR02EDTM Computation
Convert latest non-missing EX.EXENDTC where VISIT in ('Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1', 'OL-D29') to numeric
TR02SDT Computation
Convert date part of non-missing EXSTDTC where EX.VISIT='Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1') to numeric
TR02SDTM Computation
Convert non-missing EX.EXSTDTC where VISIT='Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1' to numeric
TRT01A Computation
Set to 'mRNA-1273' if at least one EX.EXTRT='mRNA-1273' where VISIT in ('Visit 1 Day 1' 'Visit 2 Day 29') and EX.EXSTDTC is not missing, Set to 'Placebo' if EX.EXTRT='PLACEBO' where VISIT in ('Visit 1 Day 1' 'Visit 2 Day 29') and EX.EXSTDTC is not missing
TRT01P Computation
Set to 'mRNA-1273' if ARM starts with 'mRNA-1273', Set to 'Placebo' if ARM starts with 'Placebo'
TRT02A Computation
Set to 'mRNA-1273' if at least one EX.EXTRT='mRNA-1273' where VISIT in ('Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1', 'OL-D29') and EX.EXSTDTC is not missing, Set to 'Placebo' if EX.EXTRT='PLACEBO' where VISIT in ('Participant Decision Visit / OL-D1', 'OL-D29')) and EX.EXSTDTC is not missing
TRT02P Computation
Set to 'mRNA-1273' where SUPPDM.QVAL='Y' and SUPPDM.QNAM='UNBLMRNA'
TRTEDT Computation
Convert date part of DM.RFXENDTC to numeric
TRTSDT Computation
Convert date part of DM.RFXSTDTC to numeric
TRTSEQA Computation
Based on TRT01AN and TRT02AN: Set to 'Placebo' if TRT01AN=1 and TRT02AN <> 2, Set to 'Placebo-mRNA-1273' if TRT01AN=1 and TRT02AN=2, Set to 'mRNA-1273' if TRT01AN=2
TRTSEQP Computation
Based on TRT01PN and TRT02PN: Set to 'Placebo' if TRT01PN=1 and TRT02PN <> 2, Set to 'Placebo-mRNA-1273' if TRT01PN=1 and TRT02PN=2, Set to 'mRNA-1273' if TRT01PN=2
TTDTH1 Computation
DTHDT - TR01SDT
TTDTH2 Computation
DTHDT - AP02SDT if AP02SDT is not missing
UBLDDT Computation
Set to date part DS.DSSTDTC where DSDECOD = 'TREATMENT UNBLINDED'
UICDT Computation
Covert date part DS.DSSTDTC where DSSCAT='Open Label' and DSDECOD = 'INFORMED CONSENT OBTAINED' to numeric
WEIGHTBL Computation
Set to the last non-missing VS.VSSTRESN where VSTESTCD = “WEIGHT” and (VSDTC is before the first vaccination (DM.RFXSTDTC) or on the first vaccination date with VSTPT contains 'PRE-DOSE'), if missing use non-missing VS.VSSTRESN where VSTESTCD='WEIGHT' and or VISIT='Screening' with VSTPT^='POST-DOSE'
ADT Computation
Convert date part of --DTC to numeric
ADY Computation
Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT + 1 if ADT is on or after ADSL.TR01SDT, Set to ADT - ADSL.TR01SDT if ADT is before ADSL.TR01SDT
AENDT Computation
Convert date part of FAENDTC to numeric if source data are from FAEF, Convert date part of PR.PRENDTC to numeric if source data are from PR, Convert date part of HO.HOENDTC to numeric if For source data are from HO
AENDY Computation
Set to AENDT - ADSL.TR01SDT + 1 if AENDT is on or after ADSL.TR01SDT, Set to AENDT - ADSL.TR01SDT if AENDT is before ADSL.TR01SDT
ASTDT Computation
For source data are from FAEF: Convert date part of SUPPFAEF.QVAL where SUPPFAEF.QNAM='FAEVDTC' to numeric For source data are from PR: Convert date part of PR.PRSTDTC to numeric For source data are from HO: Convert date part of HO.HOSTDTC to numeric
ASTDY Computation
Set to ASTDT - ADSL.TR01SDT + 1 if ASTDT is on or after ADSL.TR01SDT, Set to ASTDT - ADSL.TR01SDT if ASTDT is before ADSL.TR01SDT
ATPT Computation
Set to FAEF.FATPT if source data are from FAEF, Set to VS.VSTPT if source data are from VS, Set to null, Otherwise
AVALC Computation
Set to PR.PROCCUR if source data are from PR Set to HO.HOOCCUR if source data are from HO For SDTM.FAEF as source data: Set to 'Y' if FAEF.FASCAT='COVID-19' and FAEF.FASTRESC in ('MILD', 'MODERATE', 'SEVERE') Set to 'N' if FAEF.FASCAT='COVID-19' and FAEF.FASTRESC = 'NONE' Set to FAEF.FASTRESC if FAEF.FASCAT='COVID-19 SEVERITY' For SDTM.VS as source data: Set to 'Y' if VSTESTCD='OXYSAT' and non-missing VSSTRESN<=93 Set to 'Y' if VSTESTCD='TEMP' and non-missing VSSTRESN>=38 and VSSTRESU='C'
AVISIT Computation
Set to 'Illness Visit'. For subject with multiple Illness Visit Day 1 (FA.FATPT='Day 1') on different dates, if ADT is on/after the 2nd Illness Visit Day 1 and prior to the 3rd Illness Visit Day 1 (if available), then set to 'Illness Visit 2', and so on
LNKID Computation
Set to PRLNKID if source data are from PR, or Set to --SPID in individual source data
PARAM Computation
Set to PR.PRTRT if source data are from PR Set to HO.HOTERM if source data are from HO and re-code 'ADMITTED TO ICU' to 'Admission to an intensive care unit due to SARS-CoV-2' For SDTM.FAEF as source data: Set to FAEF.FAOBJ and recode follwing symptom terms - Recode to 'Vasopressors Required' if FAEF.FAOBJ='Evidence of Shock Requires Vasopressors' Recode to 'Muscle Aches (Myalgia)' if FAEF.FAOBJ='Myalgia' Recode to 'Runny Nose (Rhinorrhea)' if FAEF.FAOBJ='Rhinorrhea' For SDTM.VS as source data: Set to 'O2 Saturation <=93%' if VSSCAT='COVID-19' and VSTESTCD='OXYSAT' and VSSTRESN is not missing and VSSTRESN<=93 Set to 'Fever' if VSSCAT='COVID-19' and VSTESTCD='TEMP' and VSSTRESN is not missing and VSSTRESN>=38
PARCAT1 Computation
Set to 'COVID-19 SEVERITY' if source data are from HO, else set to --SCAT in individual source data Re-code 'COVID-19' to 'COVID-19 SYMPTOM'
SEV Computation
For SDTM.FAEF as source data: Set to FAEF.FASTRESC if FAEF.FASCAT = 'COVID-19' and FASTRESC in ('MILD', 'MODERATE', 'SEVERE') Set to null, Otherwise
SRCDOM Computation
Set to FAEF.DOMAIN if source data are from FAEF Set to VS.DOMAIN if source data are from VS Set to PR.DOMAIN if source data are from PR Set to HO.DOMAIN if source data are from HO
SRCSEQ Computation
Set to FAEF.FASEQ if source data are from FAEF Set to VS.CESEQ if source data are from VS Set to PR.PRSEQ if source data are from PR Set to HO.HOSEQ if source data are from HO
SRCVAR Computation
Set to 'FASTRESC' if source data are from FAEF Set to 'VSSTRESN' if source data are from VS Set to 'PROCCUR' if source data are from PR Set to 'HOOCCUR' if source data are from HO
